dc_title_s: Iberian Peninsula 1:250,000: Mugia, sheet 1. Series A.M.S. M581
dc_description_s: United States. Army Map Service. North Decimal Degree 44.0000. South Decimal Degree 43.0000. East Decimal Degree -9.0000. West Decimal Degree -10.0000. Alternate title: Mugia, Spain: La Coruna Province. Polyconic projection. With Spanish-English glossary. Relief shown by 100 m. contour interval, gradient tint and spot heights. Standard map series designation: A.M.S. M581. "Compiled from Spain 1:100,000, Estado Mayor del Ejercito, sheet 7, 1917, and sheet 22, 1915; Spain 1:200,000, Cuartel General del Generalisismo, sheet 1, 1934 and sheet 11, 1935; Spain and Portugal road map 1:400,000, AMS, third edition, sheet 41, 1943; Railways in Spain and Portugal 1:1,500,000, GSGS 1941, corrected from intelligence Reports, 1942-44.".
